<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Fit-Out Request ID <%= @fitout_request.id %></title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 20px auto;
            padding: 20px;
            border: 1px solid #ddd;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }
        .header {
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #444;
            border-bottom: 2px solid #eee;
            padding-bottom: 10px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .footer {
            margin-top: 20px;
            font-size: 0.9em;
            color: #777;
        }
        strong {
            color: #000;
        }
        table {
            width: 100%;
            border-collapse: collapse;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        th, td {
            border: 1px solid #ddd;
            padding: 8px;
            text-align: left;
        }
        th {
            background-color: #f2f2f2;
        }
        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            background-color: #007bff;
            color: #ffffff;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            text-align: center;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin: 10px 0;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <%= @fitout_request.building_name %>
        </div>

        <h1>Dear <%= @fitout_request.user&.firstname %> <%= @fitout_request.user&.lastname %>,</h1>

        <p>This is in regards to your Fit-Out request (ID: <%= @fitout_request.id %>) received for your <%= @fitout_request.unit&.name %>, <%= @fitout_request.building_name %>.</p>

        <p>Please find the details of your payment below:</p>

        <table>
            <thead>
                <tr>
                    <th>REQUEST TYPE</th>
                    <th>STATUS</th>
                    <th>AMOUNT</th>
                </tr>
            </thead>
            <tbody>
                <% @fitout_request.fitout_request_categories.each do |category| %>
                <tr>
                    <td><%= category.category_type&.name || "Document Required" %></td>
                    <td><%= category.status&.humanize || "Pending Upload" %></td>
                    <td>₹ 10,000</td>
                </tr>
                <% end %>
                <% if @fitout_request.fitout_request_categories.empty? %>
                <tr>
                    <td>Fitout Security Deposits</td>
                    <td>Pending Upload</td>
                    <td>₹ 10,000</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td>Required Documents</td>
                    <td>Pending Upload</td>
                    <td>₹ 0</td>
                </tr>
                <% end %>
            </tbody>
        </table>

        <p>Kindly upload copy of all the applicable documents from the following link.</p>
        <a href="#" class="button">Upload</a>

        <p>We thank you for your association, and please let us know in case you need any further assistance.</p>

        <p>Thanking You,<br>
        <%= @fitout_request.building_name %></p>

        <div class="footer">
            <p>Powered by <strong>LOCKATED</strong></p>
            <p><em>Note: This is an auto generated email. Please do not reply.</em></p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>